<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Portal Enfermagem</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --primary: #a51b0b;
      --primary-2: #000000;
      --text: #000000;
      --muted: #222222;
      --line: #000000;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .topbar {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 18px;
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .auth a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .auth a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .nav {
      background: var(--primary-2);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 10px 18px;
    }
    .nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 22px auto;
      padding: 0 18px;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #a51b0b, #000000);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    .hero h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 30px; }
    .hero p { margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }
    .card .value {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .section {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .section h3 { margin-top: 0; }
    .links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .links a {
      display: block;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #000000;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      color: #000000;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .links a:hover { background: #f5f5f5; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 24px 0 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <h1 class="brand">Portal Enfermagem</h1>
      <nav class="auth">
        <a href="/login">Minha Conta</a>
        <a href="/cadastro">Cadastre-se</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/">Início</a>
      <a href="/procedimentos">Procedimentos</a>
      <a href="/medicamentos">Medicamentos</a>
      <a href="/terminologias">Terminologias</a>
      <a href="/quiz">Quiz</a>
      <a href="/notas">Notas</a>
      <a href="/lembretes">Lembretes</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h2>Seu apoio rápido na prática de enfermagem</h2>
      <p>Consulte conteúdos essenciais, revise protocolos, teste conhecimentos e organize sua rotina em um só lugar.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid" aria-label="Resumo">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Procedimentos</h3>
        <div class="value"><%= procedimentoCount %></div>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Medicamentos</h3>
        <div class="value"><%= medicamentoCount %></div>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Terminologias</h3>
        <div class="value"><%= termoCount %></div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h3>Acessos rápidos</h3>
      <p class="muted">Abra direto o recurso que você precisa no momento.</p>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="/procedimentos">Consultar procedimentos</a>
        <a href="/medicamentos">Consultar medicamentos</a>
        <a href="/terminologias">Ver terminologias</a>
        <a href="/quiz">Responder quiz</a>
        <a href="/notas">Gerenciar notas</a>
        <a href="/lembretes">Gerenciar lembretes</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="footer">Portal Enfermagem</div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
